ABOUT US
/$
$
Welcome to The Lagoon on Grassy Key!
We are a tropical adventure park, marketplace, and day resort located in the heart of the Florida Keys.
The Lagoon is home to Keys Cable Wakeboard Park, The Rhum Runner Aqua Park, Bongo's Botanical Beer Garden, and the Lagoon Saloon Surf Shoppe.
Come soak up the vibes!
